Name: SuperMarkdown
Version: 0.2.4
Summary: export a complex Markdown file into a standalone HTML file.
Home-page: https://github.com/madeindjs/Super-Markdown
Author: Rousseau Alexandre
Author-email: rousseaualexandre.lyon@gmail.com
